{"schemaVersion":2,"book":"2JN","name":"2 Juan","chapters":{"1":{"1":{"text":"El anciano a la señora escogida y a sus hijos, a quienes • amo en verdad, y no sólo yo, sino también todos los que conocen la verdad,","segments":[{"text":"El","morph":"DNSM","strong":"G3588"},{"text":"anciano","morph":"JNSM","strong":"G4245"},{"text":"a la señora","morph":"NDSF","strong":"G2959"},{"text":"escogida","morph":"JDSF","strong":"G1588"},{"text":"y","morph":"CLN","strong":"G2532"},{"text":"a sus","morph":"RP3GSF","strong":"G846"},{"text":"hijos","morph":"DDPN"},{"text":", a quienes","morph":"RR-APM","strong":"G3739"},{"text":"•","morph":"RP1NS","strong":"G1473"},{"text":"amo","morph":"VPAI1S","strong":"G25"},{"text":"en","morph":"P","strong":"G1722"},{"text":"verdad","morph":"NDSF","strong":"G225"},{"text":", y","morph":"CLN","strong":"G2532"},{"text":"no","morph":"BN"},{"text":"sólo","morph":"JNSM","strong":"G3441"},{"text":"yo","morph":"RP1NS","strong":"G1473"},{"text":", sino","morph":"CLC","strong":"G235"},{"text":"también","morph":"BE"},{"text":"todos","morph":"JNPM","strong":"G3956"},{"text":"los","morph":"DNPM","strong":"G3588"},{"text":"que conocen","morph":"VRAP-PNM","strong":"G1097"},{"text":"la","morph":"DASF","strong":"G3588"},{"text":"verdad","morph":"NASF","strong":"G225"},{"text":","}]},"2":{"text":"a causa de la verdad que permanece en nosotros y que estará con nosotros para siempre:","segments":[{"text":"a","morph":"P","strong":"G1223"},{"text":"causa de la","morph":"DASF","strong":"G3588"},{"text":"verdad","morph":"NASF","strong":"G225"},{"text":"que","morph":"DASF","strong":"G3588"},{"text":"permanece","morph":"VPAP-SAF","strong":"G3306"},{"text":"en","morph":"P","strong":"G1722"},{"text":"nosotros","morph":"RP1DP","strong":"G2254"},{"text":"y","morph":"CLN","strong":"G2532"},{"text":"que estará","morph":"VFMI3S","strong":"G2071"},{"text":"con","morph":"P","strong":"G3326"},{"text":"nosotros","morph":"RP1GP","strong":"G2257"},{"text":"para","morph":"P","strong":"G1519"},{"text":"siempre","morph":"DASM"},{"text":":"}]},"3":{"text":"Gracia, misericordia y paz serán con nosotros, de Dios Padre y de Jesucristo, Hijo del Padre, en verdad y amor.","segments":[{"text":"Gracia","morph":"NNSF","strong":"G5485"},{"text":", misericordia","morph":"NNSN"},{"text":"y paz","morph":"NNSF","strong":"G1515"},{"text":"serán","morph":"VFMI3S","strong":"G2071"},{"text":"con","morph":"P","strong":"G3326"},{"text":"nosotros","morph":"RP1GP","strong":"G2257"},{"text":", de","morph":"P","strong":"G3844"},{"text":"Dios","morph":"NGSM","strong":"G2316"},{"text":"Padre","morph":"NGSM","strong":"G3962"},{"text":"y","morph":"CLN","strong":"G2532"},{"text":"de","morph":"P","strong":"G3844"},{"text":"Jesucristo","morph":"NGSM"},{"text":", Hijo","morph":"DGSM"},{"text":"del","morph":"DGSM","strong":"G3588"},{"text":"Padre","morph":"NGSM","strong":"G3962"},{"text":", en","morph":"P","strong":"G1722"},{"text":"verdad","morph":"NDSF","strong":"G225"},{"text":"y","morph":"CLN","strong":"G2532"},{"text":"amor","morph":"NDSF","strong":"G26"},{"text":"."}]},"4":{"text":"¶ Mucho me alegré al encontrar algunos de tus hijos andando en la verdad, tal como hemos recibido mandamiento del Padre.","segments":[{"text":"¶ Mucho","morph":"BE","strong":"G3029"},{"text":"me alegré","morph":"VAPI1S","strong":"G5463"},{"text":"al","morph":"CAZ","strong":"G3754"},{"text":"encontrar","morph":"VRAI1S","strong":"G2147"},{"text":"algunos de","morph":"P","strong":"G1537"},{"text":"tus","morph":"RP2GS","strong":"G4675"},{"text":"hijos","morph":"DGPN"},{"text":"andando","morph":"VPAP-PAM","strong":"G4043"},{"text":"en","morph":"P","strong":"G1722"},{"text":"la verdad","morph":"NDSF","strong":"G225"},{"text":", tal","morph":"CAM","strong":"G2531"},{"text":"como hemos recibido","morph":"NASF","strong":"G1785"},{"text":"mandamiento","morph":"VAAI1P","strong":"G2983"},{"text":"del","morph":"P"},{"text":"Padre","morph":"NGSM","strong":"G3962"},{"text":"."}]},"5":{"text":"Y ahora te ruego